SEC. 5. A national committee composed of the following shall take the lead in the preparation and implementation of the guidelines on how to celebrate the week through simple and appropriate ceremonies and activities:

Chairperson of the Commission on Human Rights - Chairperson;

Chairperson of the Civil Service Commission - Vice Chairperson;

One (1) representative from each of the following government agencies as members:

Department of Education;

Department of National Defense;

Department of Justice;

Department of Social Welfare and Development;

Department of Foreign Affairs;

Department of Labor and Employment;

Department of the Interior and Local Government and

Philippine National Police.

One (1) representative each two (2) human rights nongovernment organizations as members, to be appointed by the President upon recommendation of the Commission on Human Rights.
